    "The Agent Creation function provides advanced LLM agents with different capabilities in manufacturing Algorithm 2: Chat Interaction 1: procedure CHAT(prompt, model) 2: with_f unctions ← len(function_info) > 0 3: msgs ← [] 4: if instructions then 5:msgs.append({\"role\": \"system\", \"content\": instructions}) 6: msgs.append({\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": prompt}) 7: response ← __get_response(msgs, model_, with_f unctions) 8: msgs.append(response.message) 9: f unction ← response.message.function_call.name 10: args ← json.loads(response.message.function_call.arguments) 11: f unction_response ← executables[f unction](**args) 12: return f unction_response, msgs systems for adaptability to changing requirements.",
